{"word":"G3781 - ὀφειλέτης - opheilétēs - of-i-let'-ace - Debtor","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὀφειλέτης</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>opheilétēs"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>of-i-let'-ace"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Debtor"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"கடனாளி, கடன்பட்டவன், குற்றவாளி - ஆண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"a debtor"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Masculine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (ஆண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/G3784 - ὀφείλω - opheílō - of-i'-lo/3784\">G3784</a>; an <i>ower</i>, that is, a person <i>indebted</i>; figuratively a <i>delinquent</i>; morally a <i>transgressor</i> (against God): - debtor, which owed, sinner."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G3781 - ὀφειλέτης - opheilétēs - of-i-let'-ace/3781\">G3781</a>, <a href=\"#/G3782 - ὀφειλή - opheilḗ - of-i-lay'/3782\">G3782</a>, <a href=\"#/G3783 - ὀφείλημα - opheílēma - of-i'-lay-mah/3783\">G3783</a>, <a href=\"#/G3784 - ὀφείλω - opheílō - of-i'-lo/3784\">G3784</a>"}]}